# Set 029 Session 3 (per-session-set orchestrator marker, schema v3).
# The writer also drops a self-protecting `.gitignore` inside each
# `.dabbler/` directory so consumer repos that haven't patched their
# root `.gitignore` still avoid committing marker files; this entry
# is the workspace-root belt-and-suspenders.
docs/session-sets/*/.dabbler/
# Set 031 (delegation.decision_consensus V1). The per-decision
# JSONL journal (ai_router/consensus-decisions.jsonl) stays
# committed — same precedent as router-metrics.jsonl — so the
# audit trail survives across conversations. The disk-heavy
# full-payload sibling directory (Markdown, one file per call) is
# default-on and explicitly opt-outable via
# delegation.decision_consensus.journal_full_payloads_dir: null.
ai_router/consensus-decisions/
# Set 044 (AI chat-log discovery + experiments). The scratch dir holds
# raw harvested logs / transcripts / sqlite dumps from the discovery
# runs. Lives outside the repo at C:\tmp\dabbler-log-harvest\, but the
# entry below is belt-and-suspenders against an accidental symlink /
# relocation that lands it under the repo root. See
# docs/session-sets/044-.../harvest-objectives-and-redaction.md Part 2.
dabbler-log-harvest/
# Set 060 follow-up (2026-06-11): the extension's tsc test-compile output.
# Regenerated by `npm test` (npx tsc --outDir out) on every run; the
# packaged extension ships from dist/ (esbuild), so out/ is pure derived
# churn. Untracked + ignored to end the recurring dirty-tree noise.
tools/dabbler-ai-orchestration/out/
# Set 078 (Copilot CLI hybrid-tier transport). The seat-local catalog
# lockfile is empirically probed per operator/seat (ai_router/copilot_catalog.py
# --refresh) and never shared truth across seats — same rationale as the
# local-overrides.yaml entry above.
ai_router/copilot-catalog.lock
